This new implementation of SWEEP is going to be split into several different folders, and is intended to be as modular,
and as reusable as possible. The main folders are as follows:
- Builder = Generating new paths for the robot to follow
- Movement = Calculating movement vectors to follow the given path
- Runtime = The main logic for handling several SWEEP Paths and making the movement execute
- Spline = The classes that generate individual spline segments, one class for each implementation of the spline algorithms
- Classes = The common classes that are used across the library

Task 1: Translating the old SWEEP Library into this new structure, and ensuring it works the same